  <summary>The open source AI code editor</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Visual Studio Code is a lightweight yet powerful source code editor with built-in Git integration, debugging, an integrated terminal, and rich extension support.</p>
    <p>It supports development across major programming languages and includes AI-powered features such as chat, agent mode, and next edit suggestions that adapt to your workflow.</p>
    <p>IMPORTANT: To use certain features in this flatpacked version (like the integrated terminal), please read the linked documentation.</p>
